@startuml
[*] --> Registration

state Registration
Registration : entry / Start registration
Registration : do / Process registration
Registration : exit / Registered or failed

state RegistrationDecision <<choice>>
Registration --> RegistrationDecision

state "Successful Registration" as SuccessReg
SuccessReg : entry / Registered successfully
SuccessReg : do / Proceed to login
SuccessReg : exit / Move to login state

state "Failed Registration" as FailReg
FailReg : entry / Registration failed
FailReg : do / Display error
FailReg : exit / Return to start

RegistrationDecision --> SuccessReg
RegistrationDecision --> FailReg

state Login
Login : entry / Enter credentials
Login : do / Verify user
Login : exit / Logged in

state LoginDecision <<choice>>
Login --> LoginDecision

state "Valid Login" as ValidLogin
ValidLogin : entry / User authenticated
ValidLogin : do / Allow access
ValidLogin : exit / Proceed to facilities

state "Invalid Login" as InvalidLogin
InvalidLogin : entry / Wrong credentials
InvalidLogin : do / Display error
InvalidLogin : exit / Return to login

LoginDecision --> ValidLogin
LoginDecision --> InvalidLogin

state LoggedIn
LoggedIn : entry / Access granted
LoggedIn : do / Display facilities
LoggedIn : exit / Choose facility

state FacilityChoice <<choice>>
LoggedIn --> FacilityChoice

state "Facility A" as FacilityA
FacilityA : entry / Access facility A
FacilityA : do / Use services
FacilityA : exit / Return to facilities

state "Facility B" as FacilityB
FacilityB : entry / Access facility B
FacilityB : do / Use services
FacilityB : exit / Return to facilities

state "Facility C" as FacilityC
FacilityC : entry / Access facility C
FacilityC : do / Use services
FacilityC : exit / Return to facilities

FacilityChoice --> FacilityA
FacilityChoice --> FacilityB
FacilityChoice --> FacilityC

state ActivityChoice <<choice>>
FacilityA --> ActivityChoice
FacilityB --> ActivityChoice
FacilityC --> ActivityChoice

state "Read News" as ReadNews
ReadNews : entry / View content
ReadNews : do / Display news
ReadNews : exit / Return to facility

state "Expert Content" as ExpertContent
ExpertContent : entry / View content
ExpertContent : do / Display expert info
ExpertContent : exit / Return to facility

state "Health Info" as HealthInfo
HealthInfo : entry / View information
HealthInfo : do / Display health data
HealthInfo : exit
@enduml
